OL,3,C"It is nice to be listened to": People
OL,4,Cwith stomas meet Belfast airport staff
OL,6,FManagement at Belfast International
OL,7,FAirport have met with people who have
OL,8,Fstomas after they said to UTV they had
OL,9,Fbeen humiliated and embarrassed while
OL,10,Ftrying to go through security at the
OL,11,Fairport.
OL,13,FIt came after DUP MP Carla Lockhart,
OL,14,Fwho has a relative with a stoma bag,
OL,15,Fraised the issue on their behalf.
OL,17,FShe said: "I had requested a meeting,
OL,18,Fa high level meeting with Wilson
OL,19,FJames, who are the security
OL,20,Fcontractors and the chief executive
OL,21,Ffrom the airport was there as well.
