OL,6,F"I would say it was a positive
OL,7,Fmeeting. I would say it was robust and
OL,8,Fquite informative in terms of what
OL,9,Fthey are doing and what they're trying
OL,10,Fto do to improve the situation."
OL,12,FClaire McCorry, who was one of the
OL,13,Fwomen who described her negative
OL,14,Fexperience of going through security
OL,15,Fat the airport, was also at the
OL,16,Fmeeting.
