OL,3,C"It is nice to be listened to": People
OL,4,Cwith stomas meet Belfast airport staff
OL,6,FShe said: "It's nice to be listened to
OL,7,Fand hopefully they will learn from not
OL,8,Fjust my experience, but from the
OL,9,Fexperience of the other passengers who
OL,10,Fhave come forward.
OL,12,F"This is not about being above the
OL,13,Flaw. It's not about that at all, and
OL,14,Fwe are all totally mindful that
OL,15,Fairport security is really important
OL,16,Fand also airport personnel have a job
OL,17,Fto do.
