OL,3,C"It is nice to be listened to": People
OL,4,Cwith stomas meet Belfast airport staff
OL,6,FIn a statement, the airport said:
OL,7,F"Whilst our current process is
OL,8,Fcompliant, we are thankful for the
OL,9,Ffeedback which will allow us to
OL,10,Fcontinue our discussions with the
OL,11,Fregulator to further develop those
OL,12,Fprocesses to ensure all passenger
OL,13,Fneeds are accommodated.
OL,15,F"As this is an issue for all airports,
OL,16,Fnot just Belfast International, we
OL,17,Fhave raised this with Airports UK and
OL,18,Fthe CAA, and we hope to be able to
OL,19,Fcontinue working on the issue."
